title: Taylor Tomlinson
itunes:title: Taylor Tomlinson
description: My HoneyDew this week is Taylor Tomlinson! Taylor is the oldest of four girls and her mom died when she was eight. We talk about what life was like growing up without a mom and not having many memories of her. We also talk about the engagement she broke off last year, a few months before taping her first hour special.
